Initiation #

You start the Discord-Dashboard class in a very easy way. Simply import it from the module.

js
const { Dashboard } = require('discord-dashboard')

new Dashboard(/*ENGINE*/)
    ...
RELEVANT Try to add further settings according to their order in the documentation. We do not guarantee the absence of errors if you use other orders.
